Netizens compare the patterns of revenge-seekers in China and the United States
Comments believe that China is the only country in the world with a "loyal aging population". On the one hand, this is because China's social care for vulnerable groups over the age of 45 is extremely poor;
It is also because the degree of civil organization in Chinese society is extremely low, which leads to these middle-aged and elderly unmarried and childless people becoming "invincible people" in the full sense after losing their parents and leaving the only organizational unit of "family".
